<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yǒu shéi xiàng nǐ 迦南657</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu shéi xiàng nǐ zhè yàng zhè yàng, qīng chǔ quán bèi de jiào dǎo.
 yǒu shéi xiàng nǐ zhè yàng zhè yàng, wú wēi bù zhì de guān huái.
 nǐ zǒng shì xiàng huǐ gǎi de rén, wǎng kāi yī miàn.
 jiē nà wǒ men lái dào nǐ shī ēn de bǎo zuò qián.
 nǐ shì shú zuì de gāo yáng, tiān tiān bèi fù wǒ men de zhòng dān.
 wǒ men de xīn zěn néng zěn néng bù shòu gǎn.
 zhǎng tú bá shè bù huì pí juàn, xīn zhōng chōng mǎn nǐ de zhēn píng ān.
 hèn bù néng zǒu dào tiān de jǐn tóu, bǎ nǐ de jiù ēn guǎng chuán.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>657</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>